Ranger Help for: recruit
========================

SYNTAX:      recruit <player name> (or: solicit)
USAGE:       Anywhere.

SUMMARY:
Offers to recruit another player into the Rangers guild. The target
player must be in the same room as you. You must be at least guild
level 5 to recruit. The target player will receive an invitation
they can accept or ignore.

